@startuml svc-safety-compliance--post-waivers

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#integration-context ⬆ svc-safety-compliance Integration Context]]

title POST /waivers\nGuest signs a safety waiver

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-safety-compliance" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/]] #FEE2E2
participant "Guest Profiles" as GP [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/]] #EDE9FE
participant "DocuSign API" as DS [[/actors/#docusign-api]] #F3F4F6
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-safety-compliance.html#/Waivers/signWaiver View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /waivers
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> GP : [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#get-guestsguest_id-get-guest-profile Validate guest identity]]
activate GP #EDE9FE
GP --> Svc : OK
deactivate GP

Svc -> DS : Verify digital signature
activate DS #F3F4F6
DS --> Svc : OK
deactivate DS

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Send waiver copy]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml